parameters:
Underling: I'm in charge of refining the delicious powder,
but I only turn the raw materials blended by the big boss
into powder. I don't know the detailed recipe...

Memimi: Shark Broccoli - The big boss used to work part-time
at a family restaurant, so he absolutely never shared his
own cooking recipes with anyone... Who would have thought
his commitment as a chef would actually decide the fate of
the organization...

Mayor Orca Asparagus: What are you muttering about! Have you
remembered anything that could be a clue to the delicious
powder production? If you don't know, then we have no choice
but to interrogate you!

Underling: Eek, I seriously don't know...! Please, no
torture...

Memimi: Truly, this guy knows nothing! The big boss is a
perfectionist... There's no hint or information...!

Mayor Orca Asparagus: Suspicious... In that case, both of
you are going through an interrogation course while we shoot
an adult video! The underling will go through the
"Continuous Ejaculation Course"! And Shark Duke will go
through the "Anal Licking Course"!!

Underling: Was it three years ago that Shark Broccoli-sama
was picked up by the big boss? This organization was formed
five years ago, and back then, Monster Fight didn't even
exist yet...

Memimi: I've heard that Monster Fight started about two
years ago. The big boss initially didn't intend to bring me
into the dark organization, so I'm not very familiar with
what happened at that time... I joined the organization a
year ago, and my debut in Monster Fight was half a year ago.

Underling: That's a rapid rise... Now Shark Broccoli-sama
has become one of the most important figures in the dark
organization, on the verge of unifying the city... Seriously
amazing...

Memimi: The one I must repay is not only Shark Broccoli-
sama, the big boss... but also everyone in the organization
who has walked with me and guided me at times. I truly am
grateful to the people around me...

Underling: You don't have to worry about that...! Just being
able to see you in sexy outfits and being allowed to fondle
your breasts is more than I can ask for...!

Memimi: That wasn't meant as a show of gratitude...! Damn
it... I've ended up exposing my shame to close
acquaintances... My personal relationships are... ugh...

Underling: Lord Shark... if Shark Mountain-san loses and has
to make an AV debut...! I absolutely hate that idea... I
want her to be only my Shark Mountain-san... I do want to
see her having sex, but only with me, not with anyone
else...!!

Memimi: Calm down... that's disgusting!! Stop repeating
'sex' over and over!!

Underling: But even if you say that... just watching her on
TV raping celebrities in reverse, I felt like I was going to
lose it, and now to think she has to sleep around with other
men as a routine... it does give me a bit of a hard-on,
but...

Memimi: ...Seriously, just shut up... I get where you're
coming from but...

Underling: At least take this...! It's a heart-shaped
necklace that I chose!! Please wear it and defeat Mayor
Orca...!!

Memimi: Gross... I mean... uh, I'll just accept the
sentiment... thank you...

Moved by the underling's feelings, Memimi's attack power
increased slightly...
